                            h4 The The name of the type of traffic to be retrieved
                .cell
                    pre(id="traffic6")

            block errors
                .spacer
                h2(id="errors") Errors
                h3 Any API call that fails due to a server error will return the following json document.
                .cell
                    pre(id="error1")

